Unrecognized command or argument '--json'.

Description:
  ednsv - DNS Email Validation Tool
  Checks performed (use --list-checks for details):
    - Delegation & NS
    - Basic DNS Records
    - MX Records
    - SPF (Sender Policy Framework)
    - DMARC
    - DKIM & ARC
    - Reverse DNS & FCrDNS
    - Blocklists (DNSBL)
    - DNSSEC
    - Transport Security
    - BIMI
    - Service Discovery
    - Infrastructure
    - Address Verification

Usage:
  Ednsv.Cli [<domain>] [options]

Arguments:
  <domain>  The domain name to validate (e.g., example.com) []

Options:
  -f, --format <format>              Output format: text, json, html, markdown [default: text]
  -o, --output <output>              Write output to file instead of stdout
  --no-axfr                          Disable zone transfer (AXFR) testing
  --catch-all                        Enable catch-all detection (sends probe to random address)
  --open-relay                       Enable open relay testing (probes MX servers for relay misconfiguration)
  --dkim-selectors <dkim-selectors>  DKIM selectors to probe instead of defaults (comma-separated or repeated; combined with any discovered via AXFR)
  --list-checks                      Show detailed descriptions of all checks performed
  --verbose                          Show why each check category matters alongside results
  --version                          Show version information
  -?, -h, --help                     Show help and usage information



